      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Roughly ~10 new workflow starts/sec on average.\n\n• Baseline ingest ≈ 10 QPS\n• Peak ≈ 100 QPS (10× burst)\n• If runs average ~1 min → ~600 concurrent\n• At peak, design toward up to ~60K concurrent\n\nWe must account for disk I/O, concurrency control, and reliability under load.",
