      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Write-heavy — we log state transitions and (later) node traces, plus historical/analytics\ndata.\nEntity relationships still matter though.\n\n→ Postgres for OLTP\n→ ClickHouse for OLAP (logs / traces / analytics)",
