      "strokeColor": "#0F172A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "Directed graph (from → to), cycles disallowed — it’s a DAG.\n\nResponse     → 1 in,  0 out\nStart        → 0 in,  1 out\nConditional  → 1 in,  2 out\nFunction     → 1 in,  1 out\nGeneral API  → 1 in,  1 out\nIntegration  → 1 in,  1 out",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Directed graph (from → to), cycles disallowed — it’s a DAG.\n\nResponse     → 1 in,  0 out\nStart        → 0 in,  1 out\nConditional  → 1 in,  2 out\nFunction     → 1 in,  1 out\nGeneral API  → 1 in,  1 out\nIntegration  → 1 in,  1 out",
